prompt:
<s>[INST] <<SYS>>
As a log parser, you will be provided with some log messages begin with [BEGIN] and end with [END] tags, and each token in a log message can be one of either a constant or a variable. You must abstract variables with <placeholders> remain constants as the same to extract the corresponding templates. You must print the results following the format below:
Log message:
[BEGIN] ciod: failed to read message prefix on control stream (CioStream socket to 172.16.96.116:33569 [END]
Log template:
[BEGIN] ciod: failed to read message prefix on control stream (CioStream socket to <ip_address> [END]
<</SYS>>

Log message:
[BEGIN] {input} [END]
[/INST]
